# Vike / SSR

## New pages

Add `src/pages/<route>/+Page.tsx`:

```typescript
export { Page };

function Page() {
  return <MyComponent />;
}
```

## Client-only APIs

`window`, Firebase listeners → `useEffect` or CSR-only pages (e.g. `/online`).

## Config

- `src/renderer/+config.h.ts`: `clientRouting: true`
- `react-icons` needs `ssr.noExternal` in `vite.config.ts`

## Custom HTML

Only `/online` has page-level `+onRenderHtml.tsx` for SEO meta.
